INSERT INTO debian_repository_index_packages (
                component_id,
                architecture,

                compression,
                size,
                contents,
                md5sum,
                sha1sum,
                sha256sum,

                updated_at
            ) VALUES ($1, $2::debian_repository_architecture, NULL, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
            ON CONFLICT (component_id, architecture)
            DO UPDATE SET
                component_id = $1,
                architecture = $2::debian_repository_architecture,
                compression = NULL,
                size = $3,
                contents = $4,
                md5sum = $5,
                sha1sum = $6,
                sha256sum = $7,
                updated_at = $8
